  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO PROHIBIT LAW ENFORCEMENT OFFICER FROM ARRESTING A PERSON WHEN THE OFFICER HAS PROBABLE CAUSE TO BELIEVE THAT A PERSON HAS COMMITTED A MISDEMEANOR OFFENSE; TO REQUIRE THE ISSUANCE OF A CITATION IN LIEU OF ARREST; TO PROVIDE FOR AN ARREST FOR VIOLENT MISDEMEANORS AND IN CERTAIN LIMITED SITUATIONS; TO AMEND SECTIONS 99-3-3 AND 99-3-7, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO CONFORM; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
